System configuration management scripts, manifests, etc.

Installation instructions:

Here's what's worked for me so far:

	wget -O sysconf.tgz https://github.com/bodine/sysconf/tarball/master
	tar xzvf sysconf.tgz
	cd bodine-sysconf-*
	./install.sh
	# ... Answer some questions

Requirements:
m4
puppet
